      <title>KKR 计划对医疗运输提供商 GMR 进行债务整顿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/kkr-plans-debt-overhaul-at-medical-transport-provider-gmr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR&amp;据一位知情人士透露，该公司正准备为医疗运输提供商 Global Medical Response Inc. 超过 40 亿美元的债务进行再融资，部分方法是说服债权人接受长期债务和优先股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/kkr-plans-debt-overhaul-at-medical-transport-provider-gmr</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:23:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥推进借贷 12.5 亿美元用于发展的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/chicago-advances-plan-to-borrow-1-25-billion-for-development</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市议会财务委员会周三批准了一项提议，出售高达 12.5 亿美元的住房和经济发展债券，在五年内平均分配，以刺激经济增长和提供更多经济适用房。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/chicago-advances-plan-to-borrow-1-25-billion-for-development</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
